snippet.title: Haqiqat Kya Hai: The Truth Behind Indelible Ink to Reduce Crowds at Banks and ATMs

localized.description:
Haqiqat Kya Hai: The truth behind Indelible ink to reduce crowds at banks and ATMs. Government has started an operation 'black' to stop peoples from converting black money into white.
Modi government has banned Rs 500 and Rs 1000 currency notes.
